{
  "stem": "23131.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My live in the smaller ghetto was different, because Tavia used to send a lot of-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] people that worked with him, that he had all the confidence in them, and to warn us, and to talk to my father.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father never-- he couldn't come to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To the closed ghetto he didn't come already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tavia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he used to send people with letters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Get out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't wait for another.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told you that this would happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lucky you survived, but get out, because another one will come.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the woods, I don't guarantee nothing, but at least there is a lot of trees, and you can hide under a tree, and you're free.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Here you are locked up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father didn't want to hear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one time, I was assigned to the gardens to take care of the vegetables and the fruit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not fruit, but mostly the vegetables-- tremendous gardens that supplied a lot of vegetables, potatoes, onions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they used to take us from the ghetto in the morning by police and a German.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in a certain hour-- in a certain hour we had to come back after sun-- sunset.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But you couldn't go alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "After 6 o'clock nobody, could be seen alone in the street, a Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because this was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And whoever they met-- if they met somebody, that's no-- no playing around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was right away they shot it, on the spot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I was assigned to the gardens.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my stepmother was assigned there, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was a Pollack that he watched the gardens.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was in charge of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I-- he-- she had always an idea that she'll hide in case of something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Any rumor she heard.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
